A na-asụ asụsụ Adele na etiti ọwụwa anyanwụ Ghana na etiti ọdịda anyanwụ Togo
Ọ bụ otu n'ime asụsụ ugwu Ghana Togo (nke a na-akpọkarị Togorestsprachen ma ọ bụ asụsụ Togo Remnant) nke alaka Kwa nke Niger China
Ndị na-ekwu okwu n'onwe ha, ndị Adele, na-akpọ asụsụ Gidire.
Na Ghana, Ghana Institute of Linguistics, Literacy and Bible Translation (en) (GILLBT) mepụtara mkpụrụ akwụkwọ iji sụgharịa Bible n'asụsụ Adele.
Mkpụrụ akwụkwọ Adele eji na Togo bụ otu ihe ahụ, agbanyeghị Rongier na-eji obere digraphs na ndepụta nke akwụkwọ ọkọwa okwu Adele-French ya.
